# nonebot-plugin-daily-bing

_✨ 每日必应壁纸 ✨_

![License](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/nonebot-plugin-daily-bing)
![PyPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/nonebot-plugin-daily-bing.svg)
